less and fast measuring technique will find broad\napplications in dynamic measurement environments and mass industrial testing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Dec 2017 08:21:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 00:49:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
