$ and lattice thermal conductivities, the ZrSSe\nmonolayer may have better n-type thermoelectric performance than\n$\\mathrm{ZrS_2}$ monolayer. These results can stimulate further experimental\nworks to synthesize ZrSSe monolayer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Dec 2017 12:43:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
